cURL is used to make http requests to an url.

example :
curl http://www.somedomain.com

--request
the value of the --request parameter can have differents values like GET, POST, DELETE, PUT
GET is the default parameter.
    curl --request GET 'http://yilmazhuseyin.com/blog/dev/'

--add
to add data to requests, use --data parameter.
    curl --request POST 'http://www.somedomain.com/login/' --data 'username=myusername&password=mypassword'
